{"tid":2123072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周浩鼎以被冒名為由 促政府立法監管「假新聞」","createTime":"2020-07-24T11:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T13:17:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f874e689366355d8db258bf907f8443cf7cd02e","tid":2123072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075793&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=34087b8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075793&h=be8bfba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075793</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎稱，連日來有人冒認其身份，以他的名義發佈政府即將實施「禁足令」的假消息。他今日（7月24日）召開記者會澄清事件，批評冒認者「極端無良及可恥」，造成選舉不公，要求政府未來設立「假新聞法」以監管新聞發放。"},{"pid":"045e13639b329c90bdce3cc454fb33ecca13ead4","tid":2123072,"uid":25468,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"話美國係武肺發源地果啲呢 ?"},{"pid":"900e903c4b3203c59d785d0185f7217460326aa9","tid":2123072,"uid":151313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"假新聞=對中共不利既新聞"},{"pid":"4f6baea47bd14c73dc7439e882f181c14d6f366e","tid":2123072,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"你搞到共產黨要幫你澄清兩次，你好唔好意思"},{"pid":"9e6780850cfd6901ecb79a3ec58d1265ac20e960","tid":2123072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6baea47bd14c73dc7439e882f181c14d6f366e","tid":2123072,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"你搞到共產黨要幫你澄清兩次，你好唔好意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src